                <article class="post-8220 page type-page status-publish hentry">

                    <section class="entry">
	                	<h1 style="text-align: left;">Practicing ません</h1>
<h4>&ldquo;Life&#8217;s most persistent and urgent question is, &lsquo;What are you doing for others?&rsquo;&rdquo; <span style="color: #888888;">- Martin Luther King, Jr.</span></h4>
<p>As always, be sure to keep practicing your verbs vocab list. Do it little by little and you&#8217;ll learn a lot. Try to do it all at once? Well&#8230; I&#8217;ll take little by little any day, personally.</p>
<p>For this practice, I&#8217;m going to ask you a question. You can answer in two different ways: using ます form or using ません form (ignore ました form for now). These answers are <em>your opinions</em>. There&#8217;s no right or wrong answer, unless your answer isn&#8217;t one of the two possible answers :P</p>
<p>Give it a try:</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-23.mp3">a</a> Q. にほんご　を　はなしますか？<br />
Do you speak Japanese? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink1326486435" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet1326486435'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet1326486435"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet1326486435'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink1326486435'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-24.mp3">a</a> A1. はい、にほんご　を　はなします<br />
Yes, I speak Japanese</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-25.mp3">a</a> A2. いいえ、にほんご　を　はなしません<br />
No, I do not speak Japanese</div></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-26.mp3">a</a> Q. えいご　を　はなしますか？<br />
Do you speak English? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink303465931" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet303465931'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet303465931"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet303465931'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink303465931'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-27.mp3">a</a> A1. はい、えいご　を　はなします<br />
Yes, I speak English</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-28.mp3">a</a> A2. いいえ、えいご　を　はなしません<br />
No, I do not speak English</div></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-29.mp3">a</a> Q. UFO　を　しんじますか？<br />
Do you believe in UFOs? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink1762815132" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet1762815132'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet1762815132"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet1762815132'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink1762815132'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-30.mp3">a</a> A1. はい、UFO　を　しんじます<br />
Yes, I believe in UFOｓ</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-31.mp3">a</a> A2. いいえ、UFO　を　しんじません<br />
No, I do not believe in UFOs</div></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-32.mp3">a</a> Q. テレビゲーム　を　しますか？<br />
Do you do (play) video games? <a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink349834218" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet349834218'))">Answer →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet349834218"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet349834218'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink349834218'))</script></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-33.mp3">a</a> A1. はい、テレビゲーム　を　します<br />
Yes, I play video games</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../audio/2-8-34.mp3">a</a> A2. いいえ、テレビゲーム　を　しません<br />
No, I do not play video games.</div></p>
<p>Are you getting a feel for ません now (hopefully some of those answers used ません!)? Now it&#8217;s time to learn the last one. After that, you can do a lot with your verbs knowledge (that is, if you&#8217;ve been studying your lists. You should do that!</p>
<div class="woo-sc-box tick   ">By finishing this page, you&#8217;ve practiced and learned how to answer simple verb-related questions. Do you do this? Why yes, I do!</div>
